title: Tallahassee Board of REALTORS速 2nd Annual Big Bend Habitat for Humanity 5K
text:
8:30 a.m. Saturday, Nov. 14, 2015 Categories 
Events, Fundraisers, Sports Certified 5K course, USATF cert. # FL11064EBM. Run or walk through mildly rolling terrain on newer asphalt roads that wind around wooded conservation areas, homesteads and horse corrals. Help the Tallahassee Board of REALTORS速 and all our wonderful sponsors raise money for Habitat for Humanity. This year, our goal is to raise 1/5 of the total cost of a build for a new Habitat home, or about $5000. You can help by registering for the race and sharing this run on your social media pages! This is a timed event, and awards will go to top finishers Overall, Masters, and 5-year age groups. Race Starts at 8:30 with ample parking at the scenic Centerville Conservation Community Lake House, located at 6633 Lake Pisgah Drive, Tallahassee, Florida 32308. Directions: -North on Thomasville Road -Right @ Bradfordville Rd -Left @ Centerville Rd -Left @ Conservation Dr -Go through gates (they will be open) -Right @ Lake Pisgah -Left into lake house gravel drive -Parking lot on right
